title: Dragon Ball Episodes 1-50 WMV XBOX 360
description:
These are the first 50 episodes of the Original Dragon Ball re-encoded to work with Windows Media center over the Xbox 360 Console.

All files are encoded in WMV Ver 7 and are in English with Japanese Texts.
These are the complete uncut episodes from Japan and not the \"Americanized\" episodes that were shown on the Cartoon Network

All videos are good quality and run about 250 megs a episode
